Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(178,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2B36A1&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara escaped GOD and tore the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to entrust to his old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has one stolen one of the pieces,\Nand the X Rider holds another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus does a deadly race for the\Nremaining seven pieces begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious Phantom Thief\NRhino Beetle Lupin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18\i1}Doumoto Theoretical Physics Laboratory{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, now for a slider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, why don't you come\Nin? I'll give you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm Norio!\N-Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Norio and Takashi, is it? Well, eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok, thanks!\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a piece of the blueprints for Dr. Nanbara's\Nenergy-generating invention, the RS Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanbara... To think you'd trust\Nme enough to send me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But my cancer hasn't given me long left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a lonely old nobody\Nwith no wife or children...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no choice but to\Ndo something drastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino Beetle Lupin, how goes the search for the\Nother seven pieces of Dr. Nanbara's blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, one of my beetles is gathering\Ninformation as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel for these boys, but...\Nmankind must know peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can use my Alpha Ray to transfer\Nthis blueprint onto their backs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't mind being remembered\Nas a worthess person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Images burnt in by the Alpha Ray can\Nonly be seen with a special filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I found a clue at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really?\N-Yeah, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Dr. Nanbara at a science convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one old picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was taken twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the guy who caught my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See how close he is to Dr. Nanbara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Nanbara's mentor, Dr. Doumoto.\NHe respected him more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-The experimental physicist?\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely a chance this\NDoumoto might know something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think--?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you learned,\NRhino Beetle Lupin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, my intelligence has identified an individual\Nwho likely has one of the blueprint pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my! You truly are the incarnation of\NFrance's famed phantom thief, Arsène Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is this person's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Doumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now nobody knows where this blueprint is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright boys, time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, rise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Guess I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for\Neating right after you play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, take all the\Nsweets you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you!\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you!\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourselves, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok!\N-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bye!\N-Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A rhinoceros beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have followed those boys in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what the--? Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino Beetle Lupin,\Nof GOD's Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know what I want, then you must\Nhave received a blueprint from Nanbara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you\Nmean. What blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play the fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Search the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This task is simplicity itself for one\Nnamed after the infamous Lupin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a fool underestimates Lupin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? A letter from Nanbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Out with it! Where is the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't talk...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd find you\Nhere, GOD! Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Adieu, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away, are you!? ...No,\NI need to check on Dr. Doumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is over... Please... don't\Nlet them get that blueprint...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't. But where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprint... the blueprint is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hold on! Where is the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I took too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you sneak in!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Doumoto can tell neither\Nof us where the blueprint is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is a battle\Nof wits to find it first...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A kid's glove...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought Dr. Doumoto\Ndidn't have any family?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Norio{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this Norio knows something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here it comes!\N-Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Does this belong to any of\Nyou? I got it from Mr. Doumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's yours?\N-It says 'Norio'! That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Great, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You visited Mr. Doumoto, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahuh. He gave me and Takashi\Ntea and sweets this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did Dr. Doumoto give\Nyou two anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok... So, where's Takashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be at the pool over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a rhino beetle\Non Norio's shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully, boy! Did anything\Nstrange happen at Doumoto's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...! I told you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-It hurts...\N-Then think harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered? Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We fell asleep... right\Nafter he gave us sweets...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... something happened then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Why didn't\Nyou say so sooner!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-We're closed for the day, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come for a swim, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm looking for a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... No time to explain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jeez, he thinks we're so dumb!\N-Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Takashi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right...\N-I've got something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You had sweets at Mr.\NDoumoto's house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... and then we fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell asleep? Anything strange happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Looks like I've hit a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, it looks like there's\Nsomething drawn on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it... Dr. Doumoto used some\Nsort of ray to tattoo it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's UV rays must\Nhave uncovered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, get in the water. We\Ncan't let anyone else see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird... He still hasn't come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken the boy. Nothing personal.\N--Rhino Beetle Lupin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke! The child is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino Beetle Lupin!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this on for size, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand him over, Rhino Beetle Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stubborn fellow! But\NI've no time for you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino Beetle Smokescreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-It burns!\N-It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there... Keep the heat on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool...! Give me the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll take this!\N-How dare you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just cut them down!\N-I've had enough of this! Get him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief! The kids!\N-Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino Beetle Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, try my Guillotine\NHat on for size!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This blueprint's mine,\NRhino Beetle Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he was all talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who will make up for Rhino\NBeetle Lupin's failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, are the kids stuck\Nwith those blueprints now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke told me something called a 'Sigma\NRay' can rub out Dr. Doumoto's Alpha Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Your backs are blueprint-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, it's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprints that were on these boys'\Nbacks are now in Keisuke's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But King Dark's Villain Army is\Nalready making its next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.60,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Keisuke - Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(40,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's Starfish Hitler finds a scientist couple with\Na blueprint piece, but learns they're impostors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Starfish Hitler's demonic hands reach for the coastal\Nhotel where Toubei is guarding the real couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Hellish Dictator Starfish Hitler!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider